::Epyon::

He expanded his comm link to include Starice, Alpha Dolphy, and Wizard.
"Ok. Wizard continue operations. Alpha, help the rest of the crew in
dismantaling the ship. Starice, stay there with the baby for now. But
eventually so much of the ship will be gone the baby will have to move.
You'll bring the baby to the CF. I hope this battle is done by then
though. I dont want to bring a baby into a war zone."
